                        "type": "token",
                        "kind": "DOCSTRING",
                        "text": "(** This is a docstring that OCaml <= 4.07.1 drops.\n        For some reason, when a class type begins with two docstrings,\n        it keeps only the second one.\n        This is fixed by GPR#2151. *)",
